<p><strong>Key management personnel</strong></p>
<p>Key management personnel are those persons having authority and responsibility for planning, directing and controlling the activities of the University: this comprises the Senior Leadership Team. The total compensation for the year ended 31 July 2022 (including any employers’ pension contributions) was £967,263 (year ended 31 July 2021, £922,575).</p>
